- 'fruits they've harvested' are the views and ratings the articles have received;
- 'freshness of the soil' corresponds to the year of the revision;
- 'ripeness of the fruit' refers to the number of views per article;
- 'first hundred tales' means the limit of 100 records.

- 'editorial team' refers to users whose role is 'editor'.;
